(e.g. every morning, at noon, before bed).', 'Every morning I wake up at 7 a.m. and make a cup of coffee before starting work. At noon I usually take a short break to eat lunch and stretch my legs. In the afternoon I continue with my tasks until the evening. Before bed, I like to read a book or review my plans for the next day. This routine helps me stay organized and productive throughout the week.', 90.0, 85.0, 95.0, 95.0, 91.0, 'Tu párrafo está bien estructurado y utiliza el presente simple correctamente. Has incluido las expresiones de tiempo necesarias y tu rutina diaria es clara. Sin embargo, podrías mejorar el vocabulario utilizando sinónimos o frases más variadas para enriquecer tu escritura.', 'HARD', 27, '{"score_grammar": 90, "score_vocabulary": 85, "score_coherence": 95, "score_spelling": 95, "feedback": "Tu p\u00e1rrafo est\u00e1 bien estructurado y utiliza el presente simple correctamente. Has incluido las expresiones de tiempo necesarias y tu rutina diaria es clara. Sin embargo, podr\u00edas mejorar el vocabulario utilizando sin\u00f3nimos o frases m\u00e1s variadas para enriquecer tu escritura."}'::jsonb, '2026-04-04T04:54:54.749215+00:00'::timestamptz) RETURNING "writing_attempts"."id"; args=(12, 24, 'Write a short paragraph (4–6 sentences) describing your daily routine. \nUse the present simple tense and include at least three time expressions \n(e.g. every morning, at noon, before bed).', 'Every morning I wake up at 7 a.m. and make a cup of coffee before starting work. At noon I usually take a short break to eat lunch and stretch my legs. In the afternoon I continue with my tasks until the evening. Before bed, I like to read a book or review my plans for the next day. This routine helps me stay organized and productive throughout the week.', 90.0, 85.0, 95.0, 95.0, 91.0, 'Tu párrafo está bien estructurado y utiliza el presente simple correctamente. Has incluido las expresiones de tiempo necesarias y tu rutina diaria es clara. Sin embargo, podrías 